  "original_title": "\u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1 \u0dad\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dc4\u0dcf \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0 \u0daf\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Chinese ambassador visits the great bishops",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chinese Ambassador Chi Shenhong said in Kandy that the Chinese government will continue to support Sri Lanka to rescue it from the temporary economic crisis it is currently facing.",
        "Malwatu Asgiri emphasized this after visiting the patriarchs.",
        "Although the current economic crisis in Sri Lanka will not end overnight, the Chinese government believes that Sri Lanka will be able to get out of it within a short reasonable time.",
        "In addition to the Chinese government's cooperation aid grant, the Chinese Buddhist Association has planned a program to provide aid for the revival of temples and Buddhism in this country.",
        "Although various changes took place in Sri Lanka, there was no change in Sri Lanka China friendship. The aim of the Chinese government is to maintain bilateral relations between the two countries. We believe that Sri Lanka has the ability to get out of the difficult situation. The ambassador added that the Chinese government will also support it."
      ],
